OL,3,CLake claims life of second teenager in
OL,4,Cseven weeks
OL,6,FA teenager has died after being pulled
OL,7,Ffrom a lake in Lincolnshire - less
OL,8,Fthan seven weeks after another
OL,9,Ffatality at the same spot.
OL,11,FThe 16-year-old boy got into
OL,12,Fdifficulty at Swanholme Lakes in
OL,13,FLincoln on Thursday evening, 9 July.
OL,15,FAfter being treated at the scene by
OL,16,Fparamedics, Lincolnshire Police said
OL,17,Fhe "initially responded to treatment".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
