OL,3,CLake claims life of second teenager in
OL,4,Cseven weeks
OL,6,FA force spokesperson said: "Sadly,
OL,7,Fdespite the efforts of emergency
OL,8,Fservices and hospital staff, he died
OL,9,Fat 8.50pm.
OL,11,F"His parents were with him at the
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,14,F"Our thoughts are with his family and
OL,15,Ffriends, and we send our condolences
OL,16,Fat this incredibly difficult time."
OL,18,FThe incident comes after 15-year-old
OL,19,FDeclan Sawyer drowned at Swanholme
OL,20,FLakes on 24 May.
